<img src="http://biz-file.com/c/1809/458840-625x157.jpg" alt="Planning a fundraiser: What you need to know" width="625" height="157">But while fundraising events are a great way to make money for your charitable cause, that doesn’t mean that they’re without stress. We’re not talking a church bake sale here: a full-scale, comprehensive and successful fundraiser can have as many turning cogs and moving parts as any other event. So, to help you on your way to total fundraiser joy, we’ve put together the must-knows when planning a fundraiser in our latest blog. Read it here: https://www.wrxgrp.co.za/planning-fundraiser-need-to-know/.